&lt;li&gt;Own portions of verification execution at subsystem and chip-level and create testbenches, tests and related artifacts to achieve structural and functional coverage closure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan and drive intermediate and sign-off reviews on verification test plans, execution progress and verification closure towards various silicon milestones including design freeze and tapeout&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
